Brocato America Deep Cleansing Shampoo - Imported (296 ml) Price: Rs.2600

Brocato America Deep Cleansing Shampoo Peppermint Scrub Shampoo (10 oz). Brocato Peppermint Scrub Purifying Shampoo is one of Sam Brocato?s ?Original 5? products. It is a fresh. invigorating deep cleansing shampoo that results in a clean healthy scalp which provides for better circulation and shinier healthier hair. this refreshing shampoo is formulated with 100% pure peppermint oil and an exhilarating fragrance. Peppermint Scrub Shampoo is an excellent clarifier in preparation for chemical services. Leave on the hair for three to five minutes and rinse. It can also be used as an everyday sports shampoo using equal parts of Peppermint Scrub and Splassh Shampoo. It may be used as a treatment shampoo once a week which is recommended for hard to clean hair (not recommended daily on chemically treated hair). or it can be used as a body scrub. Apply Peppermint Scrub to a loofah sponge and gently massage the entire body to leave it feeling fresh and clean.
